init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You ask the other people if they know what's going on.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "This has never happened to me before either," says another.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "It can't be broken," says the first person.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The screen goes blank for another few minutes.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I don't like this place," you say.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Don't worry, it's the Grim Reaper," says one of the other reincarnations.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Don't let him touch you," says another.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He points to a chair, and you sit down.
